text: Still Blue is the second collaborative studio album by American singer- songwriter Jared Evan and producer Statik Selektah. The project was released on October 28, 2014. The album features guest appearances by Michael Christmas, Nyck Caution, Dessy Hinds and Ransom. ==Track listing== All songs produced by Statik Selektah. ==References== Category:2014 albums Category:Statik Selektah albums Category:Albums produced by Statik Selektah Category:Collaborative albums
title: Still Blue
